'''Very Important Person''' ('''VIP''', usually pronouced V-I-P) is an individual who is accorded special privileges due to his status or importance.

Examples include [[celebrity|celebrities]], [[Head of State|heads of state]], [[High roller|high rollers]], [[politician|politicians]], [[corporate officer|corporate officers]], [[wealthy]] individuals, or any other person who receives special treatment for any reason. In some cases, such as [[ticket]]s to events, VIP status can be purchased by anyone.

